| gmt_modified       | timestamp(6)       | YES  |     | CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(6) | ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(6) |
| tenant_id          | bigint(20)         | NO   | PRI | NULL                 |                                |
